creator: Arvolear
descriptionHtml:
Zoomer is an extremely simple yet challenging game with a purpose of zooming into a mesmerizing figure called fractal.

PREPARE TO DIVE INTO THE WORLD OF ZOOMER

Rules are substantially straightforward - zoom into the game via your thumbs just as you would scale an image or a map. Stay focused, on each 10'th zoom the game becomes noticeably more challenging and difficult, however the further you progress the more immersive experience you gain.

EXPLORE THE MIND BLOWING FRACTAL

During the walkthrough you will earn coins to buy boosters of different powers and custom colors of all kinds. Boosters will enhance your zooming strength and colors will change the look of the whole game!

PURE MATHEMATICS IN DISGUISE

Behind the pristine beauty of the observed fractal lays nothing but the branch of mathematics called algebra. Consider imagining a complex numbers plane. Choose a random point on that plane and square it infinite number of times. If the output value converges, paint the chosen point black, it belongs to the set, else paint it into any other color. The recognisable fractal will be generated in the end if many points are considered.

CREDITS

Huge kudos to http://instagram.com/sokol.art_/ for making the game possible.

All the sounds used in the game are taken from http://zapsplat.com.
